---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Emergency Withdrawal — SPA earn-defi.com"
  description="How to withdraw your funds. Standard processing within 1 business day, up to 5 days for positions requiring unwinding. Contact procedures and safety guidelines."
  canonical="https://earn-defi.com/emergency-withdrawal"
>

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-5 border-b border-white/5">
    <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5 3 12m0 0 7.5-7.5M3 12h18"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="text-sm">Back to earn-defi.com</span>
    </a>
    <span class="text-xs text-white/20 font-mono">emergency-withdrawal</span>
  </nav>

  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-xs text-red-400/70 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Emergency</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Emergency Withdrawal</h1>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        How to access your funds in urgent situations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Withdrawal Policy -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">Withdrawal Policy</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          Withdrawals are processed on request. Standard processing time is usually within
          1 business day, but large withdrawals or withdrawals requiring position unwinding
          may take up to 5 business days. No withdrawal fee is planned for the MVP.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Withdrawal Procedure -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">Withdrawal Procedure</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-green-400/60 bg-green-400/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70 font-medium">Contact us directly</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40 mt-1">Email: <a href="mailto:yuriycooleshov@gmail.com" class="text-green-400/80 hover:text-green-400 underline underline-offset-2">yuriycooleshov@gmail.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-green-400/60 bg-green-400/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70 font-medium">Describe your situation</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40 mt-1">We will respond within 4 hours during business hours.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-green-400/60 bg-green-400/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70 font-medium">Funds available without unwinding</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40 mt-1">If funds are available without unwinding positions, we process as quickly as possible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-green-400/60 bg-green-400/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">4</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70 font-medium">Positions need unwinding</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40 mt-1">If positions need to be unwound, processing takes up to 5 business days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start rounded-lg border border-red-500/15 bg-red-500/5 p-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-red-400/60 bg-red-400/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">!</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70 font-medium">No guaranteed same-day withdrawal</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40 mt-1">Do not trust any source promising instant access to your funds.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Direct Protocol Withdrawal -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">Direct Protocol Withdrawal</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Because SPA deploys to established DeFi protocols (Aave, Compound, Morpho),
          your funds remain in audited, permissionless smart contracts. In an emergency,
          you can interact directly with the underlying protocol to withdraw.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/40 leading-relaxed">
          Contract addresses for direct interaction will be published before go-live.
          Currently in paper trading &mdash; no live contracts deployed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What to Do During a Frontend Incident -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">What to Do During a Frontend Incident</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start rounded-lg border border-red-500/15 bg-red-500/5 p-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-red-400/60 bg-red-400/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">!</span>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60">Do <strong class="text-white/80">NOT</strong> click any links claiming to be &ldquo;emergency&rdquo; alternatives.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-green-400/60 bg-green-400/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55">Verify official communication at <a href="mailto:yuriycooleshov@gmail.com" class="text-green-400/80 hover:text-green-400 underline underline-offset-2">yuriycooleshov@gmail.com</a> only.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-green-400/60 bg-green-400/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55">Check GitHub repository for official statement.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-green-400/60 bg-green-400/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55">Do not interact with any unverified contract.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-green-400/60 bg-green-400/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">4</span>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55">Wait for official communication before taking action.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Official Communication Channels -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">Official Communication Channels</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-green-500/20 bg-green-500/5 p-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-400/60 font-mono mb-1">Email</p>
          <a href="mailto:yuriycooleshov@gmail.com" class="text-sm text-green-400/80 hover:text-green-400 underline underline-offset-2">yuriycooleshov@gmail.com</a>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-green-500/20 bg-green-500/5 p-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-400/60 font-mono mb-1">GitHub</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60">github.com/yurii-spa/SPA</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-red-500/15 bg-red-500/5 p-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-red-400/60 font-mono mb-1">No Telegram</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/50">Any Telegram group claiming to be SPA is fake.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-red-500/15 bg-red-500/5 p-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-red-400/60 font-mono mb-1">No Discord</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/50">Any Discord server claiming to be SPA is fake.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />

</Layout>
